index_terms: DEPARTMENT OF SOCIAL AND HEALTH SERVICES
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Public Health Department; accepting certain moneys from the Washington State Department of Social and Health Services for replacement of certain obsolete equipment and purchase of new equipment and supplies for maternal and child health care purposes; establishing a "Special Projects" program category in the 1974 Budget of said Department in connection therewith; ratifying and confirming certain expenditures heretofore made; making a reimbursable appropriation from the Emergency Fund and declaring the emergency therefor.
